Class HabitType

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.util.Observable
      • com.cmput301.t05.habilect.HabitType
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class HabitType
extends java.util.Observable
implements java.io.Serializable
    This is the model for habit types. A habit type is a class describing a certain habit that the user wants to regularly do.
